(Author: Gosho Aoyama)

5
00:00:12,484 --> 00:00:14,602
A murder took place in Singapore.

6
00:00:15,218 --> 00:00:17,853
At the crime scene was a bloody notice from Kid.

7
00:00:18,405 --> 00:00:20,719
(The legendary blue sapphire)
His target is the legendary treasure.

8
00:00:21,156 --> 00:00:21,796
However...

9
00:00:22,492 --> 00:00:24,548
The strongest karate practitioner
with 400 consecutive victories,

10
00:00:25,007 --> 00:00:26,704
Makoto Kyogoku, stands in his way!

11
00:00:27,047 --> 00:00:28,832
Why are you here?

12
00:00:28,863 --> 00:00:30,423
No more talking!

13
00:00:33,312 --> 00:00:35,599
Kid, why did you bring me here?

14
00:00:35,648 --> 00:00:38,205
Tell me what's in the fist, great detective.

15
00:00:38,623 --> 00:00:42,519
What is in that mysterious fist called "murder"?

16
00:00:43,898 --> 00:00:45,601
(Magic  Truth  Kick)

17
00:00:47,102 --> 00:00:48,521
Kid, too...

18
00:00:48,695 --> 00:00:50,417
(A gigantic "darkness" begins unravelling)
will soon be done for.

19
00:00:50,516 --> 00:00:52,132
I don't want to be protected

20
00:00:52,398 --> 00:00:53,976
(Theme song: Blue Sapphire by Hiroomi Tosaka)
by a man who is full of lies!

21
00:00:54,773 --> 00:00:55,989
Hey, Shinichi.

22
00:00:56,429 --> 00:00:57,393
We're...

23
00:00:57,733 --> 00:00:59,189
dating, right?

24
00:00:59,586 --> 00:01:02,406
I know you're the mastermind behind all this.

25
00:01:02,436 --> 00:01:04,027
(Special Guests:
Ikusaburo Yamazaki  Mayuko Kawakita)

26
00:01:04,058 --> 00:01:06,396
A legendary treasure that was buried
at the bottom of the ocean

27
00:01:06,906 --> 00:01:07,743
has travelled across time

28
00:01:07,984 --> 00:01:10,026
and awakened the darkness within Singapore!

29
00:01:10,172 --> 00:01:11,089
He can't be!

30
00:01:11,127 --> 00:01:12,000
(An era...)

31
00:01:12,390 --> 00:01:14,810
This time, you must not leave my side!

32
00:01:14,944 --> 00:01:15,998
(comes to an end.)

33
00:01:16,109 --> 00:01:17,905
Stealing a treasure

34
00:01:18,187 --> 00:01:19,478
is my job!

35
00:01:20,195 --> 00:01:21,907
Don't die, Kid!

36
00:01:22,617 --> 00:01:24,319
Detective Conan The Movie!

37
